    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Overview</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dad is taking a well-deserved break from work to recharge at home. Before he goes back to being the great dad that he is, he needs some relaxation. Your job is to help him unwind during his bath time by feeding him the right snacks. But be careful—Dad has picky tastes! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Enjoy Variety of Wears</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137300/extras/86b33978b1a7a25288671da966f30525.poster.avif?t=1771608144\" width=616 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137300/extras/86b33978b1a7a25288671da966f30525.webm?t=1771608144\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137300/extras/86b33978b1a7a25288671da966f30525.mp4?t=1771608144\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>How to Play</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- <strong>Objective</strong>: Keep Dad happy and relaxed by feeding him his favorite foods while avoiding the yucky ones. Score points to unlock amazing Wears for Dad!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- <strong>Gameplay</strong>:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  1. Pick the Right Food: Select the tasty snacks that Dad loves from a variety of options.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  2. Watch out!: Make sure the food doesn’t get past him.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  3. Avoid Yucky Food: Discard any food that Dad doesn’t like. If you accidentally feed him something yucky, Dad’s relaxation level will decrease.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  4. Score Points: Earn points for each correct food you feed or discard for Dad.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  5. Unlock Wear: Reach high scores to unlock cool and fun wears for Dad to wear during his bath time.</p>",
